---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Easter egg | Portafolio</title>
    <script is:inline>
      try {
        if (sessionStorage.getItem('studio-door-transition') === '1') {
          document.documentElement.dataset.doorTransition = '1';
          sessionStorage.removeItem('studio-door-transition');
        }
      } catch {}
    </script>
    <style is:inline>
      html[data-door-transition="1"],
      html[data-door-transition="1"] body {
        background: #000 !important;
      }

      html[data-door-transition="1"] body > * {
        visibility: hidden !important;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="content-page easter-page">
    <main class="content-shell">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">Volver al estudio</a>
      <p class="eyebrow">Easter egg</p>
      <h1>Modo secreto desbloqueado.</h1>
      <section class="content-grid">
        <article>
          <h2>Mini juego pendiente</h2>
          <p>Este espacio queda preparado para meter un juego pequeño o una sorpresa interactiva.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
    <script is:inline>
      if (document.documentElement.dataset.doorTransition === '1') {
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
          window.setTimeout(() => {
            delete document.documentElement.dataset.doorTransition;
          }, 260);
        }, { once: true });
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
